  "what": "Cross-reference of v1 complex DockQ (gold-standard interface quality) with the leakage audit, testing whether LEAKAGE-CLEAN complexes still fail at docking -> i.e. whether protein-complex interface prediction is a viable specialist-FAILURE substrate (routing stakes) under leakage control.",
